We made plenty of bug fixes to improve the stability of the app. A few notable issues fixed with this release: Fix issue with some in app purchase not registering Reduce frequent disconnects. Thanks for supporting the app. Please tell your friends about it and leave us a good review.

Performance enhancements and bug fixes. Reduce frequency of ads. Show keyboard immediately when chat starts. There is a bug with sending photos on the iPAD on iOS 9. This bug will be fixed in the releasing following this one.
Many IOS 9 bug fixes Fix Bluetooth popup dialog issue. Support changing username Support playing music in background while chatting.

Bug fixes and performance enhancements. fixed issue with new users not being able to see elite upgrade until relaunch of app. fixed issue with app crashing when specifying age. Please support us and leave us a good review. Good reviews give us fuel to make the app even better.
add pro features to elite subscription add age range filter for match preferences bug fixes and performance enhancements Please give us a 5 start review. We would love your support.

Resolve issue with Elite status not showing correct of days remaining. When your elite status elapsed the app was showing the of days since it elapsed as the of days remaining. We have also fix many issues that were crashing the app. This version should be more more stable.

Add support to specify your gender. Fixed a long listed of performance bugs. Redesign user interface. Add indication that other user has terminated a conversation. Please if you like the app leave us a glowing review. It would mean a lot to us.
